'''尼诺·舒尔特'''（德语、{{lang-rm|Nino Schurter}}，{{bd|1986年|5月13日||}}）生于格劳宾登州卢姆内齐亚，是一名瑞士男子自行车运动员，主攻山地自行车<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.brujulabike.com/nino-schurter-34-birthday/|title=Nino Schurter, the king of MTB XCO, celebrates his 34th birthday|work=Brujula Bike|date=2020-05-13|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/nDKH9|archivedate=2020-09-23}}</ref>。他童年时时常被家人带到山上去，他也在7岁时开始接触山地自行车<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.london2012.com/athlete/schurter-nino-1127875/|title=Nino Schurter|work=London 2012|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030223616/http://www.london2012.com/athlete/schurter-nino-1127875/|archivedate=2012-10-30}}</ref>。2007年，他加入[[斯科特體育|Scott]]-[[速联|Sram]] MTB Racing队，成为职业车手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nsracing.ch/index.php?page=659|title=About me|website=nsracing.ch|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815010844/http://www.nsracing.ch/index.php?page=659|archivedate=2012-08-15}}</ref>。2018年，他获得年度最佳瑞士男运动员奖<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lalasport.com/2018/12/nino-schurter-beats-federer-as-swiss.html|title=Nino Schurter beats Federer as Swiss sportsman of the year|work=Lala Sport|date=2018-12-11|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/N7Jon|archivedate=2020-09-23}}</ref>。

